  "aeroworks.ponder.mechanical_servo.header": "Controlling Rotational Angles using Mechanical Servos",
  "aeroworks.ponder.mechanical_servo.text_1": "Mechanical Servos relay a rotational angle based on the input redstone signal",
  "aeroworks.ponder.mechanical_servo.text_2": "Right-click to configure its rotation range",
  "aeroworks.ponder.mechanical_servo.text_3": "At full signal strength, the Servo rotates to the end of its range",
  "aeroworks.ponder.mechanical_servo.text_4": "The Servo rotates to an angle proportional to the signal strength",
  "aeroworks.ponder.mechanical_servo.text_5": "Before responding to a new signal, the Servo will finish its current rotation",
  "aeroworks.ponder.stepper_servo.header": "Controlling Rotational Angles using Stepper Servos",
  "aeroworks.ponder.stepper_servo.text_1": "Stepper Servos rotate to an angle proportional to the signal strength",
  "aeroworks.ponder.stepper_servo.text_2": "Right-click to set the angle of each step",
  "aeroworks.ponder.stepper_servo.text_3": "A stronger signal rotates the Stepper more",
  "aeroworks.ponder.stepper_servo.text_4": "Before responding to a new signal, the Stepper will finish its current rotation",
